text.paragraph:
Administer the following dosing regimens for cephalexin capsules to patients with impaired renal function [see 
                              Warnings and Precautions (5.4) and Use in Specific Populations (8.6)
                           ].

list.item:
•
Clostridium difficile-associated diarrhea [see Warnings and Precautions (5.2)
]
